# Input

```scss
@forward"theme";

@forward "theme"show
$color,
button;

@forward
"theme"
hide
$private,
internal-mixin;

@forward "theme"as
theme-*;

@forward "theme" with(
$spacing:4px !default,
$radius: 2px
);

@forward "theme" as theme-* show
$color,
button
with(
$spacing:4px
);

```


# Formatted

```scss
@forward "theme";

@forward "theme" show $color, button;

@forward "theme" hide $private, internal-mixin;

@forward "theme" as theme-*;

@forward "theme" with (
	$spacing: 4px !default,
	$radius: 2px
);

@forward "theme" as theme-* show $color, button with ($spacing: 4px);

```
